div(aria-live="polite" aria-atomic="true" id="popover")
	.toast(style="position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0;" data-autohide="false")
		.toast-header
			svg.rounded.mr-2(width="20" height="20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice"
				focusable="false" role="img")
					rect(fill="#007aff" width="100%" height="100%")
			strong.mr-auto Bootstrap
			small 11 mins ago
			button(type="button" class="ml-2 mb-1 close" data-dismiss="toast" aria-label="Close")
				span(aria-hidden="true") &times;
		.toast-body
			| Hello, world! This is a toast message.